<p>The story of Cascadian Farm starts over 40 years ago with Gene Kahn. Gene was an idealistic 24-year-old graduate school dropout who wanted to make a difference in the world. So he founded a small, organic farm on a little stretch of land in beautiful Skagit Valley, Washington. That farm quickly grew and became a pioneer in the burgeoning organic food industry. Today, Cascadian Farm has grown well beyond the home farm, but Gene's mission continues: to bring you delicious, organic food you can believe in, food like Cascadian Farm Organic Blueberries.</p>
